type: software
title: "civil-judgment-taiwan-vectorstore"
abstract: >
  An OpenClaw skill for ingesting Taiwan civil court judgments (民事判決)
  into Qdrant using Ollama embeddings. Supports deterministic chunking,
  section-aware parsing, metadata extraction (cited norms, reasoning snippets,
  candidate issues), and incremental upserts for RAG-based legal research.
